How to Buy #XRP ?

XRP is one of the largest and most popular cryptos on the market, so it’s really easy to buy XRP. You can invest in XRP coins on almost every crypto exchange in the world, including Binance, KuCoin, Bithumb, FTX, Bybit, Bitstamp, Huobi Global and many more.

However, the current XRP price of around $0.6 is still much lower than its ATH (All Time High) of $3.84 achieved in January 2018. There’s a great chance that when the SEC lawsuit is finally over, XRP price will try to revisit these levels soon.
Many skeptics were convinced that the lawsuit will mark the end of XRP. However, this was not true and legal issues didn’t stop XRP from retaining its strong market position.

After almost 10 years on the market, XRP is still one of the top 10 largest coins in the world.

One of the reasons why XRP was able to achieve such success is the fact that Ripple Labs Inc. was able to acquire important partners among world’s leading financial institutions.

When Was XRP Founded?

XRP was created in 2012, just three years after Bitcoin, by a company called Ripple Labs Inc. led by Chris Larsen and Jed McCaleb. This makes XRP one of the most time-tested cryptocurrencies in the blockchain ecosystem.
Furthermore, XRP is a very eco-friendly cryptocurrency, and the XRP network doesn’t require huge amounts of electric energy to operate.

Although XRP is not as decentralized as Bitcoin, it has many other massive advantages. XRP transactions are very fast and cheap - they usually take only a few seconds, and the transaction cost is so low that transactions are practically free.

What Is XRP?

XRP is a technologically advanced digital currency developed by Ripple Labs Inc. Because of that, some people call the cryptocurrency itself “Ripple” or “Ripple coin”, but that is incorrect - the coin’s name is simply XRP.
But what is XRP exactly, what’s so unique about it, and is it still worth it to buy XRP in 2022?

#XRP for Beginners:🧵
For many years, XRP was one of the most popular and most influential altcoins in the blockchain ecosystem. Out of the numerous cryptocurrencies on the market, XRP managed to achieve huge success and gain significant adoption.
